data.author: vamshi konduri
data.message:
Increase friction coefficient (#9)

Default friction of 0.3 causes robots like husky to slip significantly causing users to be confused. higher friction should reduce these issues. Sample application for testing husky is in this world at https://github.com/aws-samples/multi-robot-fleet-sample-application.
